# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Skoutt — .env.example
# Copy this to .env and fill in your credentials.
# All SKOUTT_ variables override config/config.toml values.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── API Keys ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SKOUTT_APIS__CLAUDE_API_KEY=sk-ant-REPLACE_ME
SKOUTT_APIS__APOLLO_API_KEY=REPLACE_ME
SKOUTT_APIS__HUNTER_API_KEY=REPLACE_ME

# ── SMTP (Outgoing Email) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
SKOUTT_EMAIL__SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SKOUTT_EMAIL__SMTP_PORT=587
SKOUTT_EMAIL__SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
SKOUTT_EMAIL__SMTP_PASSWORD=your-app-password
SKOUTT_EMAIL__FROM_NAME=Track Exhibits
SKOUTT_EMAIL__FROM_EMAIL=your-email@gmail.com

# ── IMAP (Incoming Email / Reply Monitoring) ──────────────────────────────
SKOUTT_IMAP__HOST=imap.gmail.com
SKOUTT_IMAP__PORT=993
SKOUTT_IMAP__USERNAME=your-email@gmail.com
SKOUTT_IMAP__PASSWORD=your-app-password
SKOUTT_IMAP__MAILBOX=INBOX

# ── Alerts ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SKOUTT_ALERTS__USER_EMAIL=your-personal-email@gmail.com

# ── Optional Overrides ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SKOUTT_DATABASE__PATH=data/skoutt.db
# SKOUTT_EMAIL__DAILY_LIMIT=60
# SKOUTT_APIS__CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-3-5-haiku-20241022
# SKOUTT_CONFIG=config/config.toml

# ── Deep Research API Keys (all optional) ─────────────────────────────────
# SerpAPI — preferred for news search (~$50/month for 5000 searches)
# SKOUTT_RESEARCH__SOURCES__SERP_API_KEY=YOUR_SERPAPI_KEY

# Google Custom Search — fallback if SerpAPI not configured
# SKOUTT_RESEARCH__SOURCES__GOOGLE_API_KEY=YOUR_GOOGLE_KEY
# SKOUTT_RESEARCH__SOURCES__GOOGLE_CX=YOUR_SEARCH_ENGINE_ID

# Disable deep research entirely (e.g., during initial testing)
# SKOUTT_RESEARCH__ENABLED=false
